Here are the extracted sentences that meet the criteria:


Tissue selective androgen receptor modulators of the present invention typically have IC50 values of 1 micromolar or less.
The ligands are added at this point, at a range of 100 nM to 0.03 nM, 10 dilutions, at a concentration on 10X, 1/10th volume, (example: 10 microliters of ligand at 10X added to 100 microliters of media already in the well.)
Tissue selective androgen receptor modulators of the present invention typically agonize repression typically with submicromolar EC50 values and Emax values greater than about 50%.
IC50S are calculated using R1881 as a reference.
